Package com.vmware.nsx.idfw

Class IdfwFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.nsx.idfw.IdfwFactory
  • public class IdfwFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    IdfwFactory is responsible for creating instances of services contained inside the com.vmware.nsx.idfw package and also has the subpackages reference to access respective subpackage services.
